def calculate_sequence(N: int) -> int:
    ans = 1

    def recursion(digits, count):
        if digits > N:
            return
        temp = 1
        for i in range(digits):
            temp *= count
            count += 1
        nonlocal ans
        ans += temp
        recursion(digits + 1, count)
    recursion(1, 1)
    return ans
